measures.name: _measures.pveb
_measures.customer_balance
measures.content:
measure customer_balance = ```
			
			VAR _current_customer = SELECTEDVALUE(accounts_open[customer_code])
			VAR _balance = CALCULATE(MAX(cotacoes_aberto[customer_balance]), cotacoes_aberto[customer_code] = _current_customer)
			VAR qtt_customer = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(accounts_open), FILTER(ALL(accounts_open),accounts_open[customer_code] = _current_customer))
			
			
			RETURN 
			IF(ISINSCOPE(accounts_open[customer_code]), DIVIDE(_balance, qtt_customer), DIVIDE(_balance, 1))
			```
